{"tid":1269413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港警察會唔會覺得羞恥？","createTime":"2019-06-30T14:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T18:09:21.000Z","uid":18628,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb32400bd447cda68d91708de7640d7b5b4c52ad","tid":1269413,"uid":18628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"撐警班人大部分都講普通話 盲既都知收錢<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野潮汕/佛山聯會 <br />\n<br />\n仲請埋劉馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知係咪有心玩鳩你地<br />\n<br />\n多人遊行 但係大部分都唔係香港人 <br />\n<br />\n換句說話黎講你地得唔到香港人既支持呀<br />\n<br />\n到底你地off duty夠唔夠膽同人講你係警察？<br />\n<br />\n多日既選擇性執法已經令到香港人對警察冇晒信心<br />\n<br />\n警察係咪諗緊反正市民都對我地反感 咁我地都唔駛顧形象亂鳩咁拉/打人啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">都係個句 今晚煲底見</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"730373277df019f9987fa7e3d903adceaa36abf8","tid":1269413,"uid":45953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:25:42.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"c5d868e3c89780b910ae6b3fbab42c9a208943bd","tid":1269413,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"會考得個位分數仲想佢地有人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a94102b8d99e051dd9dd0c582b7faee8099f778","tid":1269413,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:26:46.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"2cee5faba9a9d13a0ec5b024884284af35b0568a","tid":1269413,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔會啦<br />\n會就唔會做"},{"pid":"9a173c07daae1a04490987be756ca4db123612b8","tid":1269413,"uid":18628,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"外國啲警察個個都讀過書 大部分都degree/master 仲要related to犯罪心理學等等 先有入場卷可以考警察<br />\n<br />\n反觀香港班毅進仔 一事無成 法例/ordinance/order等等都背唔到就比佢地做執法者<br />\n<br />\n外國叫police officer，班毅進仔竟然夠膽跟風又叫自己做officer 唔知不知廉恥都唔知點形容"},{"pid":"5214246d4b66659fcad3a2f3723f4be9c